                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Hunter</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1899-04-26">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 26, 1899</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Hunter reports having discussed the Pears matter with the chargé d’affaires
                    of Honduras, who, after advising his Government, suggests arbitration, and asks
                    if such a proposition should be entertained.)</p>
            </div>
